eachother...though I did go to a social once a long time ago and it kinda
put me off (you meet some wierdos). You're on Povar eh? I just spoke to a gu
at EB in Westlake Center who plays a gnome rogue (not a common sight) on

Oh yeah, I was there to FINALLY get EQ! WOOOO...bout freakin time. Still
don't know what server I'm gonna be on, but a BIG thanks to all of you who
posted info on servers! Maybe I'll see some of you online =)
